OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHospitals to introduce     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMartha's rule from April   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hospitals in England will be offered   
OL,6, funding from April to introduce        
OL,7, "Martha's rule", the NHS has announced.
OL,9,FThe government has backed plans to roll
OL,10,Fout a system giving seriously ill      
OL,11,Fpatients easy access to a second       
OL,12,Fopinion if their condition worsens.    
OL,14,FAbout two-thirds of hospitals - at     
OL,15,Fleast 100 - will initially be able to  
OL,16,Fapply to participate in the scheme.    
OL,18,FIt follows a campaign by the parents of
OL,19,FMartha Mills, 13, who died of sepsis   
OL,20,Fbecause her symptoms were missed.      
